           <lb n="7" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">tunā</supplied> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"></gap> <gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"></gap> <unclear>ha</unclear>thin<unclear>ā</unclear> sah<unclear>ā</unclear> sāveṇa <unclear>ni</unclear>kasabadhi
