         <div type="translation">
 	<p n="1-2">Success! On the 10th day of the 5th fortnight of the hot season in the 8th year of the king Maḍhariputa Svāmisakaseṇa. On the above (date).</p>
    <p n="3-5">A cave is established of (by) the market councilor and householder ++?ti, son of the market councilor Veṇhunadi of Kalyan.</p>
    <p n="5-7">Together with the noble Nada, together with the father Veṇhunadi, together with the mother Bodhisamā, together with the brother <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"></gap> <gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"></gap> <unclear>ha</unclear>thi, together with the entire (group) of his own relatives….</p>         
         </div>
          
          
          
          
